    "管理 Worker 的环境变量与密钥，随手增删改。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Manage a Worker’s environment variables and secrets — add, edit, and remove on the fly."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "管理 Worker 的環境變數與密鑰，隨手增刪改。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK": {
